Refactor pads.html: extract widget/overlay sections into template fragments

Extract 6 large HTML sections from pads.html and the reboot overlay from
network.html into reusable _-prefixed fragment files:

- _widget_bar_chart.html  → {{WIDGET_BAR_CHART}}
- _widget_gauge.html      → {{WIDGET_GAUGE}}
- _widget_sparkline.html  → {{WIDGET_SPARKLINE}}
- _style_help.html        → {{STYLE_HELP}}
- _health_widget.html     → {{HEALTH_WIDGET}}
- _reboot_overlay.html    → {{REBOOT_OVERLAY}}

Update tools/minify-web-assets.sh to load and substitute all 6 new
placeholders alongside the existing HEADER/NAV/FOOTER/BINDING_HELP ones.

No behavioral changes — the rendered HTML output is identical.

